					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-779828#post-1975594</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-779828/scp-2592#post-1975594</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 23 Feb 2014 22:34:36 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Aelanna</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>334454</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Most autonomous or living entities &#8212; particularly ones that show mind-affecting properties &#8212; automatically preclude being Safe by nature of their ability to stop cooperating with us. By the <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/mackenzie-glossary">locked box test</a>, living entities also can't be Safe because we can't lock it in a box and forget about it; if we do, it'll eventually die through starvation.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
