					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-779828#post-1974038</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-779828/scp-2592#post-1974038</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 21 Feb 2014 20:41:15 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Communism will win</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>617958</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>First:</p> <blockquote> <p>capable of telepathic community</p> </blockquote> <p>Second: what exactly does it plan to <em>do</em> with milk and bananas? It doesn't even have a mouth. For that matter, the page doesn't address how the hell this thing is even alive.</p> <p>Third: The first description paragraph is too long. I suggest splitting it up.</p> <p>Fourth: The recovery story seems shoehorned into an SCP that wouldn't have much going for it otherwise.</p> <p>Fifth: That picture is laughably small. <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">I distinctly recall seeing a larger version on the original article.</span> My recollection seems to be wrong. Still, it's too small.</p> <p>Downvoted.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
