				<pubDate>Fri, 21 Feb 2014 20:25:43 +0000</pubDate>
								<wikidot:authorUserId>1361261</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I would ordinarily no-vote this. It's well-written stylistically per usual standards, it's a serious article which we apparently need desperately more of, and the milk-and-bananas thing is handled in such a way that we're not hammered over the head with the implications here. With a little more depth I would upvote, but I'm not quite there yet.</p> <p>I am downvoting, however, as I just can't maintain any suspension of disbelief when the main picture is straight from the ED creepypasta page. Find a different picture and/or remove the picture, and I'll neutral vote.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
